n her to travel around the world, presenting her work in places such as Spain, Germany and the interior of the Mexican Republic.  In 2020 the actress landed an important role in the Netflix original series, Historia de un crimen: La Búsqueda, Said production revives the case of little Paulette, a story that shocked Mexico and, in addition, gave a glimpse of the journalistic and governmental dynamics that complicated the case from the beginning. Verónica is also part of the cast of Backdoor, a comedy project that was born on the internet and went viral in 2019, because of the video Harina, in which Verónica played Lieutenant Ramírez.","name":"Verónica Bravo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Verónica es una actriz, cantante y escritora mexicana que ha desarrollado su carrera en el teatro y la televisión. Se graduó del Centro Universitario de Teatro (CUT) de la UNAM en 2012. Desde entonces se ha labrado una carrera en las tablas que le ha valido el aprecio del público, destacándose en proyectos como La Vengadora de las Mujeres, dirigida por Carla Soto en Almagro, España; Cómo Sembrar Cocodrilos en un Cabaret Mecánico; Los Equilibristas; Demasiado Cortas las Piernas; Visceral, un monólogo sobre una niña que ha perdido a su madre y, La madriguera, dirigida por José Sampedro.  El teatro la ha llevado a viajar por todo el mundo, presentando su obra en lugares como España, Alemania y el interior de la República Mexicana. En 2020 la actriz consiguió un papel importante en la serie original de Netflix, Historia de un crimen: La Búsqueda, dicha producción revive el caso de la pequeña Paulette, una historia que conmocionó a México y, además, dejó entrever las dinámicas periodísticas y gubernamentales que complicaron el caso desde un principio. Verónica también forma parte del elenco de Backdoor, un proyecto de comedia que nació en internet y se viralizó en 2019, por el video Harina, en el que Verónica interpretó a la Oficial Rosario Ramírez.","name":"Verónica Bravo","primary":true}}]}},"tv_278096_credits":{"at":1773688734321,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":3520407,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Wen Moyan","original_name":"溫茉言","popularity":0.5736,"profile_path":"/lTXFwMpAzuLE2XedCHwVyPVT4VR.jpg","character":"Su Qingran / Wen Yueqian / Qianyue","credit_id":"6744ee8b100e4f4524fbcc61","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":4389265,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Sun Chengxiao","original_name":"孙丞潇","popularity":0.2417,"profile_path":"/4jdFtnahyQzovngOloMcN0gU3kY.jpg","character":"Wanyan Jin","credit_id":"6744ef6546260e14fbeb5b2a","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":3994845,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Gan Wangxing","original_name":"甘望星","popularity":0.7132,"profile_path":"/173XD8VZrCnIW1hMF226NvHkNpD.jpg","character":"Yan Shaoxuan","credit_id":"6744ef71cc1d69986bd9ec4c","order":2},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":3508415,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Chen Jieyi","original_name":"陈洁怡","popularity":0.2897,"profile_path":"/2vbc3dR1WSuFeJmI9E9oU5PqemL.jpg","character":"Su Feiyi","credit_id":"6744f118100e4f4524fbcd18","order":3},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2892507,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Wang Zexuan","original_name":"王澤軒","popularity":0.6216,"profile_path":"/oIr4ic07NuMROhKvzUN6wavr8Yv.jpg","character":"Wanyan Qi","credit_id":"692fabed1a0ce1811d1725fc","order":4},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":4189487,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Li Linfei","original_name":"Linfei Li","popularity":1.0076,"profile_path":"/12KQrquG12ntNihvR8Ioq1YwX1.jpg","character":"Zhi Jin","credit_id":"696660f28ae3a365e04c15a1","order":5},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":3998514,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Wu Jifeng","original_name":"Jifeng Wu","popularity":0.389,"profile_path":"/hPY2nc3AJfkz6BCtBKBBZ7IK2HN.jpg","character":"Gong Shixian","credit_id":"69666189808629e8dacc9898","order":6},{"adult":f